          TerraLib 5 - Common Runtime Module
          ==================================
                 (UNDER DEVELOPMENT)
          
This folder contains the source code of the common rutime module
of TerraLib.

Module Dependencies:
--------------------

This is the basic module of TerraLib and doesn't depend
on other modules.

The third-party software needed:
1. Boost.FileSystem
2. Boost.Locale
3. Boost.Thread
4. Apache log4cxx
5. Gnu Iconv
6. Gnu Gettext

All that dependencies can be turned off
in Linux configure, or in VC++ windowsplatformdefines.h file.

More Information:
-----------------

The TerraLib 5 wiki contains a complete explanation about
the internals of this module:
http://www.dpi.inpe.br/terralib5/wiki/doku.php?id=wiki:designimplementation:common


